      <p><a href="ch73s47.html#MonstersAnimals183">Wolves</a> are pack hunters known for their persistence and cunning.<a href="img/MonstersAnimals.Wolf.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersAnimals.Wolf.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
