        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersAnimals184"/>
        <p>A favorite tactic is to send a few individuals against the foe's front while the rest of the pack circles and attacks from the flanks or rear.</p>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2325970"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersAnimals185"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Trip (Ex):</strong></span> A <a href="ch73s47.html#MonstersAnimals183">wolf</a> that hits with a bite attack can attempt to trip the opponent (+1 check modifier) as a free action without making a touch attack or provoking an attack of opportunity. If the attempt fails, the opponent cannot react to trip the <a href="ch73s47.html#MonstersAnimals183">wolf</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2326022"/>
