          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersAnimals186"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Skills:</strong></span> *<a href="ch73s47.html#MonstersAnimals183">Wolves</a> have a +4 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills303">Survival</a> checks when tracking by scent.</p>
